  "text": "BTP can be therefore treated as a vital regulatory mechanism, allowing for effective self-regulation of various affect-related outcomes. Individuals with highly balanced temporal perspectives experience more positive moods [CITATION_1] , lower stress and anxiety [CITATION_2] , and lesser PTSD after traumatic experiences [CITATION_3] .",
